high_descs: Go to the counter behind you and the the right of the sink.
Pick up the pan that is to the right of the hand soap.
Take the pan to the fridge behind you.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Go to the counter next to the fridge.
Place the pan on the counter next to the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on the counter.

high_descs: turn to face the toaster, go towards the toaster, turn left, go towards the sink
turn around and go to the refrigerator across the room
open the refrigerator, place the pan on the top shelf, close the refrigerator door, wait 7 seconds, open the refrigerator, take the pan from the top shelf, and close the refrigerator door
turn left, go forward to the toaster, and turn to face the toaster
place the pan to the left of the toaster
anns.task_desc: Place a cool frying pan next to the toaster

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Grab the frying pan to the right of the soap dispenser.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on your left.
Put the frying pan in the fridge, close the fridge, wait a while, and then take the pan out of the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the kitchen cabinet with the toaster on top of it.
Place the frying pan on top of the kitchen cabinet and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold frying pan next to the toaster.
